ol2/iss1/9" title="Attributive Modifiers in Taglennaa (Kordofan Nubian)">Attributive Modifiers in Taglennaa (Kordofan Nubian)</a><br /><span class="auth">Ali Ibrahim and Angelika Jakobi</span></span></div><span style="font-size: x-small;">   </span><br /><div class="doc"><div class="pdf"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://digitalcommons.fairfield.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1019&amp;context=djns" title="PDF is 568 KB"><acronym title="Portable Document Format">PDF</acronym></a></span></div><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://digitalcommons.fairfield.edu/djns/vol2/iss1/10" title="Kadaru-Kurtala Phonemes">Kadaru-Kurtala Phonemes</a><br /><span class="auth">Thomas Kuku Alaki and Russell Norton</span></span></div><span style="font-size: x-small;">   </span><br /><div class="doc"><div class="pdf"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://digitalcommons.fairfield.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1024&amp;context=djns" title="PDF is 274 KB"><acronym title="Portable Document Format">PDF</acronym></a></span></div><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://digitalcommons.fairfield.edu/djns/vol2/iss1/11" title="Tabaq Kinship Terms">Tabaq Kinship Terms</a><br /><span class="auth">Khaleel Ismail</span></span></div><span style="font-size: x-small;">   </span><br /><div class="doc"><div class="pdf"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://digitalcommons.fairfield.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1026&amp;context=djns" title="PDF is 749 KB"><acronym title="Portable Document Format">PDF</acronym></a></span></div><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://digitalcommons.fairfield.edu/djns/vol2/iss1/12" title="An Initial Report on Tabaq Knowledge and Proficiency">An Initial Report on Tabaq Knowledge and Proficiency</a><br /><span class="auth">Khalifa Jabreldar Khalifa</span></span></div><span style="font-size: x-small;">   </span><br /><div class="doc"><div class="pdf"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://digitalcommons.fairfield.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1022&amp;context=djns" title="PDF is 482 KB"><acronym title="Portable Document Format">PDF</acronym></a></span></div><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://digitalcommons.fairfield.edu/djns/vol2/iss1/13" title="Number Marking on Karko Nouns">Number Marking on Karko Nouns</a><br /><span class="auth">Angelika Jakobi and Ahmed Hamdan</span></span></div><span style="font-size: x-small;">   </span><br /><div class="doc"><span style="font-size: x-small;">  </span><br /><div class="pdf"><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://digitalcommons.fairfield.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1015&amp;context=djns" title="PDF is 297 KB"><acronym title="Portable Document Format">PDF</acronym></a></span></div><span style="font-size: x-small;">  </span><span style="font-size: x-small;"><a href="http://digitalcommons.fairfield.edu/djns/vol2/iss1/14" title="Nubische Berichtigungsliste (1)">Nubische Berichtigungsliste (1)</a><br /><span class="auth">Grzegorz Ochała and Giovanni Ruffini</span></span></div></blockquote></blockquote><blockquote class="tr_bq"><blockquote class="tr_bq"><a href="http://digitalcommons.fairfield.edu/djns/vol1/iss1/"><span style="font-size: x-small;">Volume 1 (2014) </span></a></blockquote></blockquote><div style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: small;">See the full <a href="http://ancientworldonline.blogspot.com/2012/07/alphabetical-list-of-open-access.html">List of Open Access Journals in Ancient Studies</a></span><br /><br /><span style="font-size: small;">And see AWOL's Roundup: <a href="http://ancientworldonline.blogspot.com/2010/08/open-access-nubia.html">Open Access Ancient Nubia and Sudan&nbsp;</a></span> </div>]]></content>
